name: Hilton Club West 57th Street New York
description:
The luxury shops of Fifth Avenue and scenic Central Park are only steps from this Midtown Manhattan hotel, offering spacious studio and suite accommodations.

Hilton Club West 57th Street New York places guests in the heart of the city and within walking distance of Broadway and Radio City Music Hall. Rockefeller Center, Times Square and many of New York City's most famous attractions are also easily accessible.

Completely non-smoking accommodations at the Hilton Club West 57th Street feature large floor-to-ceiling windows, offering stunning views of the city. Guests can also enjoy the state-of-the-art fitness centre as well as 24-hour front desk service.

name: WestHouse Hotel New York
description:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at WestHouse Hotel New York! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.
Located in Midtown Manhattan, this hotel is an 8-minute walk from Times Square and a 3-minute walk from Central Park. The hotel features multiple luxury amenities, including a lounge bar with premium alcoholic and non alcoholic beverages, continental breakfast, and Wi-Fi access.

Featuring luxury bedding, each room at the WestHouse Hotel New York includes a flat-screen cable TV, a tablet and a desk. Free premium toiletries, a hairdryer, and a professional hair styling tool can be found in the en suite bathroom.

Guests staying at the WestHouse Hotel New York can enjoy additional luxury amenities including a 24-hour reception area, 24-hour business centre services, concierge services, digital newspapers and magazines, and bottled water.

The Terrace is private to hotel guests and features two spacious lounge areas with views of Manhattan and the Hudson River.
